{"tid":222010,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"世界咁大容不下兩隻貓..","createTime":"2017-04-29T07:35:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-06T15:02:06.000Z","uid":39745,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9c206e878c67d2d9b57549f659cc7414e8e206ee","tid":222010,"uid":39745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T07:35:37.000Z","msg":"事緣係我屋邨樓下有養兩隻貓仔<br />\n唔經唔覺已經養左有一年<br />\n其中一隻仲唔小心生埋bb 但老闆兩公婆好好有搵人領養<br />\n之後都有幫兩隻貓女做返絕育<br />\n平時兩隻貓會係個籠附近生活 因為有綁繩<br />\n而且清潔都做足 識得係貓沙柯 唔會周圍大小便<br />\n<br />\n佢兩隻貓都經常有人去睇同玩 都幾受歡迎<br />\n但附近就有間鋪<br />\n好唔鍾意兩隻貓 搵人投訴要令兩隻貓消失<br />\n問題係 兩隻貓唔算公眾地方養<br />\n鋪主同左另一間鋪商量放兩隻貓係佢倉門口養<br />\n而平時都唔會攪到第二間鋪<br />\n<br />\n單單只係唔鍾意 就要令兩隻貓消失？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/0NIUPJO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F0NIUPJO.jpg&h=d08c15b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/f2nsVln.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Ff2nsVln.jpg&h=e4a2cea1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9c9261618335a033aefc82d18864a37c18c77680","tid":222010,"uid":63670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T07:37:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f6b2ed99dac8358330c8ec01bf8e48e58795202","tid":222010,"uid":39745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T07:37:51.000Z","msg":"大眾女友，成日幻想養佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/110081/page/1?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/110081/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n呢個係等之前post過既貓貓相"},{"pid":"3d6f2c093b653f8b94ed518257e6257fc8cd9a75","tid":222010,"uid":39745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T07:38:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大眾女友，成日幻想養佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/110081/page/1?ref=ios\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/110081/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n呢個係<span style=\"color: red;\">我</span>之前post過既貓貓相</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個間所謂天美<br />\n人美又如何？個心係黑色嫁"},{"pid":"903ca788650545825d03f67ee23b17f11a181437","tid":222010,"uid":39745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T07:42:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我知道呢個消息後勁嬲<br />\n我有問過老闆娘<br />\n如果真係唔養得會點？<br />\n佢話一係放養  但一定會好坎坷。因為之前菜檔有隻貓就係放養但俾人吊死 非常殘忍<br />\n一係俾人領養..<br />\n唉"},{"pid":"278632351a83b19ed2e74177b1b417cfb8c5dfa7","tid":222010,"uid":37093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T07:44:08.000Z","msg":"又唔係走入佢間鋪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />關佢撚事咩 人地養貓都要管"},{"pid":"26cd58608f38e8ec01f8ca62119b4fb401cfef4b","tid":222010,"uid":105534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T07:46:39.000Z","msg":"山景邨？？？"},{"pid":"a0c1826ab186070578fba060c2901e772977ab47","tid":222010,"uid":39745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T07:48:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又唔係走入佢間鋪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />關佢撚事咩 人地養貓都要管</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/c2g87Oo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fc2g87Oo.jpg&h=4132d540&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢只會跳上側邊裁縫舖<br />\n但兩間鋪好fd 所以無問題<br />\n佢有綁繩 根本唔會煩到其他人"},{"pid":"53fe5ef1176412a4e2f4712fe993822a10697c28","tid":222010,"uid":39745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T07:48:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>山景邨？？？</blockquote><br />\n係 我本身上個post都唔想自爆<br />\n但呢件事忍無可忍"},{"pid":"5e188a410f92f8ef4e711b823a73512ca75e4652","tid":222010,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T08:02:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又係呢啲仆街廢中<br />\n少少野都容唔到"},{"pid":"f7d11e6d1c0ea937ef7ab14c2c0eb649c9693b28","tid":222010,"uid":105534,"like":0